Connection 

Arduino Uno1 Pin	Connected Component

A0	Soil Moisture A0
A4	HTU21D SDA
A5	HTU21D SCL
D4	Pump Relay IN
D5	2-Relay IN1 (fan)
D6	2-Relay IN2 (misting)
5V	Soil Sensor, Relays, HTU21D 

Arduino Uno2 Pin	Connected Component

A0	ADXL335 X-axis
A1	ADXL335 Y-axis
A2	ADXL335 Z-axis
A4 (SDA)	BH1750 I2C Data
A5 (SCL)	BH1750 I2C Clock
D8	Buzzer
D9	Servo 1
D10	Servo 2
3.3V	ADXL335 Power
5V	BH1750 Power, optionally Servo Power
GND	Common ground
